title: Baby has her cakes and eats it too in this hilarious cake smash photo shoot
text:
Baby has her cakes and eats it too in this hilarious cake smash photo shoot originally appeared on goodmorningamerica.com

Quinn Wallace is a baby who knows what she wants. And what she wants is cake.

When her parents planned a cake smash photo shoot for her first birthday, they thought she'd "pull a piece off and try it," her mom Audra Wallace told "Good Morning America."

But instead, Quinn did exactly what we all wish we could whenever a cake presents itself in front us. She took the whole thing.

(More: Why more moms are turning to 'black-market' baby formula)

Her mom caught the hilarious moment on video and sent in for the "GMA Moment."

(More: This 'baby shark' just won Halloween so the rest of us can go home now)

The Key Largo, Florida, mom said she didn't know her daughter would be so excited by the cake, though she "loves food in general and is a great eater."

When Quinn gets older, Wallace said she'll tell her "she’s been a girl that knows what she wants, from the beginning, just like her mom."
